<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.1.10">
<l>peṟṟa māḷiyai pērilma ṇāḷaṉai</l>
<l>kaṟṟa nūlkali kaṉṟiyu raiceyta</l>
<l>coṟṟi ṟamivai colliya toṇṭarkaṭ</l>
<l>kaṟṟa millaiyaṇ ṭamavark kāṭciyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For devotees who recite this group of verses</l>
<l>Composed by Kalikaṉṟi who has studied texts,</l>
<l>About the groom in Pēr with huge mansions,</l>
<l>There is no suffering; the universe is their dominion.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
